text: Spectacle Lake is a lake in Isanti County, in the U.S. state of Minnesota. It was so named on account of its outline being shaped like a pair of spectacles. Spectacle Lake Wildlife Management Area is next to the lake, midway between the cities of Princeton and Cambridge, Minnesota. ==See also== *List of lakes in Minnesota ==References== Category:Lakes of Minnesota Category:Lakes of Isanti County, Minnesota
title: Spectacle Lake (Minnesota)
